Nama keluarga saya bukan Xi.

483
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:09,790
Seorang pelanggan wanita kata
nama keluarga awak Xi.

484
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:12,270
Rupa dan perwatakan yang
digambarkan olehnya,

485
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:14,000
semuanya sama seperti awak.

486
00:25:14,310 --> 00:25:17,070
Cuma umur tak sepadan.

487
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:19,440
Dia kata orang itu seorang lelaki tua.

488
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:22,440
Betul.

489
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:24,210
Sayalah lelaki tua itu.

490
00:25:26,030 --> 00:25:27,360
Apa lagi yang dia cakap?

491
00:25:27,900 --> 00:25:29,920
Dia telah sediakan bilik dan makanan

492
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,240
untuk awak,

493
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:34,200
tetapi bilik ini agak kecil.

494
00:25:35,110 --> 00:25:37,350
Namun, pelanggan wanita itu kata
awak sudah tua

495
00:25:37,350 --> 00:25:38,550
dan sukar berjalan.

496
00:25:39,030 --> 00:25:39,830
Dia berpesan khas kepada awak

497
00:25:39,830 --> 00:25:43,090
agar berhati-hati dengan anak tangga
semasa naik tangga.

498
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:46,110
Saya tengok awak tak nampak macam pun.

499
00:25:46,110 --> 00:25:47,590
Kalau begitu, ikut saja
apa yang dia cakap.

500
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:49,650
Baiklah, pelanggan, sila ikut sini.

501
00:25:55,220 --> 00:25:56,300
Maaf, pelanggan.

502
00:25:56,410 --> 00:25:59,500
Makanan ini juga diaturkan oleh
pelanggan wanita itu.

503
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:02,440
Dia kata awak sudah berumur 60 tahun,

504
00:26:02,490 --> 00:26:03,580
gigi tak kuat,

505
00:26:03,610 --> 00:26:05,410
jadi dia minta awak makan bubur.

506
00:26:08,830 --> 00:26:09,720
Beri saya seteko arak lama.

507
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:10,290
Baiklah!

508
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:12,550
Seteko arak lama!

509
00:26:18,860 --> 00:26:21,520
Yanbei dan negara Yong berperang
setiap tahun,

510
00:26:21,690 --> 00:26:24,000
perniagaan kulit semakin susah dijalankan.

511
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,200
Semua lauk telah dihidangkan.

512
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:27,680
Kos pengangkutan ulang-alik saja

513
00:26:28,240 --> 00:26:29,840
telah meningkat beberapa kali ganda.

514
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:31,240
Sudah tiada untung lagi.

515
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,650
Asyik berperang setiap tahun,

516
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:37,820
perniagaan rumah penginapan saya
pun tak baik.

517
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:39,300
Eh, betul juga.

518
00:26:39,790 --> 00:26:41,640
Baru-baru ini, Yanbei dan negara Yong

519
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:43,190
mahu bertukar tawanan perang.

520
00:26:43,190 --> 00:26:46,790
Sebab itu, pelanggan yang datang
dan pergi lebih ramai sebaliknya.

521
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:48,240
Bukankah negara Yong dan Yanbei

522
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,500
berperang selama ini?

523
00:26:49,750 --> 00:26:50,830
Kenapa tiba-tiba

524
00:26:51,130 --> 00:26:52,920
mahu bertukar tawanan perang
pada masa ini,?

525
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,590
Khabarnya, dalam kalangan
tawanan perang ini

526
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:56,160
ada bekas Tentera Anggun.

527
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,500
Chu Qiao telah hilang.

528
00:26:57,510 --> 00:26:59,240
Maharaja Yan mahu memancing
Chu Qiao keluar,

529
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:00,830
jadi baginda sanggup melakukan
apa-apa saja

530
00:27:00,830 --> 00:27:02,630
untuk bertukar tawanan perang.

531
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:03,720
Kamu dah dengar?

532
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:04,720
Maharaja Yan ini

533
00:27:04,790 --> 00:27:07,880
boleh dianggap wira muda
yang sangat berkuasa.

534
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:10,720
Tetapi, perasaan baginda terhadap
panglima wanita Chu Qiao itu

535
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,960
memang sangat mendalam.

536
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:14,790
Chu Qiao itu

537
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:17,720
telah dibunuh oleh panglima negara Yong,
Zhuge Yue.

538
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:19,940
Dikatakan Chu Qiao ini

539
00:27:19,970 --> 00:27:21,830
pernah menjadi hamba wanita
keluarga Zhuge.

540
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:24,320
Keluarga Zhuge ini memelihara hamba
secara turun-temurun.

541
00:27:24,320 --> 00:27:25,790
Terutamanya, Zhuge Yue ini

542
00:27:25,790 --> 00:27:27,680
ialah pewaris keluarga mereka.

543
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:30,200
Entah berapa ramai hamba wanita

544
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,980
yang telah dibunuh oleh mereka.

545
00:27:31,980 --> 00:27:33,690
Hidup dan mati dikawal oleh orang lain.

546
00:27:33,690 --> 00:27:34,950
Sungguh menyedihkan.

547
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:37,200
Namun, tuhan itu adil.

548
00:27:37,370 --> 00:27:39,500
Dia juga telah mati di dasar tasik ais.

549
00:27:51,030 --> 00:27:51,720
Tuan,

550
00:27:51,810 --> 00:27:53,910
lokasi tepat Panglima He
telah dikenal pasti.

551
00:27:53,910 --> 00:27:55,930
Cuma kota Lin ini wilayah negara Yong.

552
00:27:55,930 --> 00:27:57,960
Mungkin ramai Tentera Yong
yang kenal awak.

553
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:59,920
Tentera Helang Hitam
juga ditempatkan berdekatan.

554
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,070
Tindakan kita

555
00:28:01,570 --> 00:28:02,720
mudah menarik perhatian.

556
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:07,680
[Kem Tawanan Kota Lin,
Sempadan Yanbei Negara Yong]

557
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:06,230
Negara Yong akan bertukar tawanan perang

558
00:28:06,230 --> 00:28:07,870
dengan Yanbei esok.

559
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:10,160
Mereka pasti takkan biarkan He Xiao

560
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:11,830
ditimpa kemalangan pada malam sebelumnya.

561
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:14,550
Xiao Ran hanya perlu membakar
di sudut kem tawanan perang,

562
00:28:14,550 --> 00:28:16,880
He Xiao pasti akan dipindahkan ke
tempat lain.

563
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:17,590
Pergi!

564
00:28:17,670 --> 00:28:19,270
Cepat! Cepat ambil air!

565
00:28:19,290 --> 00:28:19,900
Dah siap.

566
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:22,550
Jom.

567
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:23,830
Kita ikut mereka.

568
00:28:24,110 --> 00:28:26,350
Tengok ke mana mereka akan berpindah.

569
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:33,030
Empat jam kemudian, masa langit kabur,

570
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:35,760
itulah masa kesedaran manusia
paling tak jelas.

571
00:28:35,790 --> 00:28:38,790
Pada masa itu, saya akan masuk
dan selamatkan He Xiao.

572
00:28:39,030 --> 00:28:39,680
Xiao Ran,

573
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:41,910
awak bantu kami di luar kota.

574
00:28:42,590 --> 00:28:43,450
Fang Miaomiao,

575
00:28:43,880 --> 00:28:46,790
awak pergi ke Pelabuhan Baichuan
untuk sediakan kapal.

576
00:28:46,790 --> 00:28:48,720
Kita akan pergi melalui jalan air.

577
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:56,170
Tiba-tiba berlaku kebakaran
pada tengah malam.

578
00:28:56,300 --> 00:28:57,980
Pelik betul.

579
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:01,680
Siapa itu?

580
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:03,160
Jika awak nak hidup,

581
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:05,770
bawa saya jumpa Komander Tentera Anggun,

582
00:29:05,830 --> 00:29:06,830
He Xiao.

583
00:29:07,030 --> 00:29:07,680
Awak...

584
00:29:08,510 --> 00:29:09,840
Di mana dia sebenarnya?

585
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:10,550
Di...

586
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:12,440
Di dalam.

587
00:29:12,570 --> 00:29:13,960
Jika awak berani tipu,

588
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:16,110
saya akan bunuh awak di sini.

589
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:17,200
Jalan.

590
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:20,640
He Xiao yang tak guna.

591
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:23,160
Awak dah bunuh begitu ramai orang
negara Yong,

592
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:24,690
masih harap untuk ditukar?

593
00:29:25,930 --> 00:29:26,760
Jangan harap!

594
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,880
Biarpun mahu bertukar tawanan perang,

595
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,680
saya akan melumpuhkan awak
terlebih dahulu.

596
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,340
Apabila awak balik ke Yanbei,

597
00:29:32,350 --> 00:29:34,610
awak akan jadi orang cacat seumur hidup!

598
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:38,960
Di dalam.

599
00:29:47,260 --> 00:29:48,020
Di mana dia?

600
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,400
Di dalam.

601
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:50,750
He Xiao ada di dalam.

602
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:01,240
He Xiao.

603
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:02,830
He Xiao.

604
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:19,290
Panglima Cheng,

605
00:30:19,750 --> 00:30:21,480
nasib baik awak ingatkan kami.

606
00:30:21,750 --> 00:30:22,750
Jika tak, hari ini

607
00:30:23,550 --> 00:30:25,750
kami akan kehilangan banduan penting.

608
00:30:28,020 --> 00:30:29,500
Cepat padamkan api!

609
00:30:29,090 --> 00:30:30,500
[Empat jam yang lalu]

610
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:31,880
Kurung semua tawanan perang
di dalam penjara kayu!

611
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:32,510
Cepat!

612
00:30:32,790 --> 00:30:33,550
Tuan Liu.

613
00:30:33,790 --> 00:30:34,310
Cepat!

614
00:30:34,330 --> 00:30:35,050
Siapa itu?

615
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:37,880
Saya Cheng Yuan,
Komander Tentera Helang Hitam Yanbei.

616
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:38,540
Dah datang!

617
00:30:39,310 --> 00:30:40,770
Laporan rasmi menyatakan

618
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:43,050
bahawa orang yang mengiringi
tawanan perang dari Yanbei

619
00:30:43,050 --> 00:30:45,110
ialah panglima tentera Yanbei, Shi Yan.

620
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:47,680
Apa niat Panglima Cheng datang?

621
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,550
Tuan Liu memang baik hati.

622
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,650
Diri sendiri pun dalam bahaya,

623
00:30:52,110 --> 00:30:53,640
masih nak risaukan saya.

624
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,370
Apa maksud awak?

625
00:30:57,640 --> 00:31:00,720
Tuan Liu fikir kebakaran ini
satu kebetulan?

626
00:31:01,270 --> 00:31:03,200
Jika pindahkan tawanan sekarang,

627
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:05,370
kamu akan masuk perangkap penjahat.

628
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:06,200
Chu Qiao,

629
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:09,040
awak pergilah dengan lega hati.

630
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:28,290
Xing Er!

631
00:31:28,630 --> 00:31:29,430
Zhuge Yue?

632
00:31:29,690 --> 00:31:30,820
Bunuh Zhuge Yue!

633
00:31:51,100 --> 00:31:51,690
Jom!

634
00:31:52,190 --> 00:31:53,390
Ada pembunuh upahan!

635
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:08,750
Cepat! Teruskan cari!

636
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:10,880
Cepat!

637
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,160
Kenapa?

638
00:32:19,090 --> 00:32:20,480
Kita perlu berpecah untuk bertindak.

639
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:22,030
Jika tak, kita terlalu menarik perhatian.

640
00:32:22,030 --> 00:32:23,000
Awak ikut jalan sana.

641
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:25,030
Saya akan ke jalan besar di depan
untuk alihkan perhatian pengejar.

642
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:27,030
Kita jumpa di luar pintu kota barat.

643
00:32:27,270 --> 00:32:27,880
Baik.

644
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:35,480
Fang Miaomiao dan yang lain berada
di Pelabuhan Baichuan.

645
00:32:35,480 --> 00:32:36,720
Jika awak tak nampak saya,

646
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:37,960
kita jumpa di pelabuhan.

647
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:38,550
Baik.

648
00:32:43,470 --> 00:32:44,270
Jangan risau.

649
00:32:44,620 --> 00:32:45,220
Pergilah.

650
00:33:05,070 --> 00:33:06,200
Geledah dengan teliti!

651
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:07,400
Jangan terlepas sebarang petunjuk!

652
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,240
Cari mereka!

653
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:09,110
Baik!

654
00:33:16,350 --> 00:33:17,030
Zhuge Yue.

655
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:19,390
Zhuge Yue.

656
00:33:23,210 --> 00:33:23,900
Zhuge Yue.

657
00:33:25,790 --> 00:33:26,720
Awak kena racun.

658
00:33:28,890 --> 00:33:29,750
Ada bunyi di sana.

659
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:31,010
Semua orang ikut saya!

660
00:33:32,030 --> 00:33:32,470
Jalan.

661
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:33,690
Cepat jalan.

662
00:33:40,310 --> 00:33:41,000
Mereka di sana.

663
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:41,510
Kejar!

664
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:57,060
Di sana, cepat kejar!

665
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:08,969
Mereka di sana!

666
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:14,960
Xing Er.

667
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:16,230
Awak...

668
00:34:17,230 --> 00:34:18,000
Zhuge Yue,

669
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:20,170
kita akan sehidup semati.

670
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:24,030
Di sana!

671
00:34:25,409 --> 00:34:26,150
Berhenti!

672
00:34:38,750 --> 00:34:40,210
Tebing ini sangat tinggi.

673
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:41,650
Jika terjun pasti mati.

674
00:34:41,650 --> 00:34:42,510
Kita berundur.

675
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:49,860
Kenapa awak seorang saja?

676
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:50,520
Di mana puteri?

677
00:34:50,520 --> 00:34:51,360
Saya tak nampak puteri.

678
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:52,480
Perintah berkurung telah dilaksanakan
di kota.

679
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:53,400
Bukan saja tentera negara Yong,

680
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:54,630
Tentera Helang Hitam juga sedang
memburunya.

681
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:55,800
Kenapa ada Tentera Helang Hitam?

682
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:56,550
Saya pun tak tahu.

683
00:34:56,550 --> 00:34:58,590
Sekarang kita mesti cari jalan
untuk selamatkan puteri.

684
00:34:58,590 --> 00:34:59,520
Panglima Cheng.

685
00:35:02,670 --> 00:35:04,760
Luka panglima teruk tak?

686
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,670
Biar saya panggil tabib untuk panglima.

687
00:35:06,670 --> 00:35:08,000
Tak perlulah, Tuan Liu.

688
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:09,510
Cuma luka luaran.

689
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:10,570
Takkan mati.

690
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:14,110
Saya ada ubat luka

691
00:35:14,630 --> 00:35:16,110
yang digunakan oleh kerabat diraja
negara Yong.

692
00:35:16,110 --> 00:35:18,110
Selepas sapukan, dalam masa tiga hari,

693
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:20,510
luka akan sembuh dengan sendirinya.

694
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:22,160
Ia sangat berharga.

695
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:26,330
Terima kasih, Tuan Liu.

696
00:35:26,550 --> 00:35:27,360
Sama-sama.

697
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:31,400
Hari ini, nasib baik Panglima Cheng
membantu sedaya upaya,

698
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:32,960
baru saya tak kehilangan banduan penting.

699
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:35,670
Saya, Liu amat bersyukur.

700
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:43,230
Sayangnya,

701
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:46,320
mereka terlepas.

702
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,190
Tuan Liu.

703
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,220
Jika awak masih hidup,

704
00:35:50,710 --> 00:35:53,310
akan ada orang tahu
apa yang berlaku malam ini.

705
00:35:53,770 --> 00:35:54,570
Kalau begitu,

706
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:56,940
saya pun tak dapat hidup lagi.

707
00:36:21,740 --> 00:36:22,530
Chu.

708
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,670
Dunia ini memang yang kuat
menindas yang lemah.

709
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,440
Tak pernah ada keadilan.

710
00:36:26,740 --> 00:36:27,380
Xing Er.

711
00:36:27,710 --> 00:36:29,280
Sama ada di syurga atau neraka,

712
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,480
kita sehidup semati.

713
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:32,230
Demi maharaja baharu Yanbei,

714
00:36:32,230 --> 00:36:32,920
bersulang.

715
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,880
Awak asyik kata awak menyukai saya.

716
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:37,070
Penipu!

717
00:36:39,370 --> 00:36:40,160
Awak ingat,

718
00:36:40,350 --> 00:36:43,610
lain kali jangan sembunyikan apa-apa
daripada saya lagi.

719
00:36:44,530 --> 00:36:45,480
Bunuh dia.

